Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.46,0:00:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zanpakuto…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their shape and abilities are\Nbased on their Soul Reaper's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.65,0:00:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reapers gain power
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.81,0:00:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by learning their names\Nand synergizing with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.93,0:00:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are born with Soul Reapers\Nand die with Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what Zanpakuto are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:01:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reign over the Frosted Heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.65,0:02:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.09,0:02:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Above you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:36.10,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE PREVIOUS DAY
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.93,0:03:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's a nice weapon\Nyou've got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.29,0:03:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to see whose is stronger,\Nyours or mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Kazeshini!\N– Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Quit playing around," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.93,0:03:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! C'mon! C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.93,0:03:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.05,0:03:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Kazeshini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting quite good at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No…nothing…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is it over already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abarai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry we're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:04:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey's big butt always\Nslows us down, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– No, that's okay…\N– I wasn't at fault for being
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– It wasn't much of\N– late today! It was Renji's!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a Sword Beast, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sword Beasts have been appearing\Na lot less frequently lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps there are only\Na few of them remaining…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.77,0:04:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reconstruction of Seireitei\Nis making progress,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so things look like they're\Nfinally getting back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been eating nothing\Nbut sweets lately—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're the one\Nwho's gotten fatter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a growing boy, so it's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.32,0:04:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I together are one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're still growing,\Nthen so am I!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.79,0:04:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Sword Beast just now…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It returned to sword form even\Nthough I never struck a fatal blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lovely moon, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright for my liking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.85,0:05:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now there's something new.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing you guys hanging out.\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.61,0:05:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing\Nunusual about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our masters hang out quite often.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your masters, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.93,0:05:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something happen to\Nyour beloved masters?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.71,0:05:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's in love with his master?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're asking for a reaping!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.89,0:05:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay. It was just a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we came here\Nto discuss something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.05,0:06:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Signs of that Sword Beast\Nhave appeared…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm positive…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.73,0:06:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Sword Beast was sucked dry\Nof its Spiritual Pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and returned to sword form\Nbefore my very eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's his doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sword Beasts were\Noriginally Zanpakuto
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that lost their masters\Nand became wild…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have a finite amount\Nof Spiritual Pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and eventually lose\Ntheir power and disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.33,0:06:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're one step away\Nfrom dying out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this guy is able to\Ntake Spirit Energy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from other Zanpakuto\Nand make it his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm able to do that,\Nas well, though…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What makes him troublesome\Nis that he was one of
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,those very rare Zanpakuto that\Nfar surpassed his master's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that troublesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To him, his master was a nuisance\Nfrom the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.69,0:06:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that his master died, he can\Nshow off his powers to the fullest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, he's using\Nhis overwhelming strength
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.85,0:07:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to take in the power of others to\Nbecome even more powerful…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.38,0:07:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the worst kind of enemy\Nthe Soul Reapers could have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.57,0:07:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at it another way…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we defeat this guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Sword Beast hunts\Nwill come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a grand finale for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waitress!\NAnother round, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.41,0:07:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.05,0:07:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rangiku, too much alcohol\Nis poison to the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm well aware of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not a child who\Ndoesn't know when to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you know me well, Haineko…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Geez… Oh, those two…\N– Hey stop it, don't get so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead—you can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.69,0:08:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sharing the orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So tell me, why'd you bring Captain\NKyoraku's Zanpakuto with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're part of the same squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the other half?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.49,0:08:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is drinking with\Nthe Captain at the barracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're okay with leaving\Nthe two of them together alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is there to worry about\Nwith a Zanpakuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to have a meal\Nwith everyone like this
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.61,0:08:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,every once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The food seems to taste better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinamori…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.81,0:08:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't touched your sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here today to enjoy\Nthe food, so no thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you\Nwon't accept my sake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop giving Momo a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.32,0:09:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right, Tobiume.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, let's all calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll accept your sake.\NWill that do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.41,0:09:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with you, Haineko?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awfully\Nlevel-headed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.89,0:09:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's because\NI'm a mature woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's my Zanpakuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well said!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.65,0:09:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you could learn\Nsomething from her, Rangiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.77,0:09:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rangiku, pull yourself together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't drink another drop…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief…she always\Nends up like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to take in\Nthe night breeze for a bit…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I leave Rangiku with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.41,0:09:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, sure, that's fine…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our apologies, Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.21,0:09:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.12,0:09:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to talk with\Nyour friends sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:09:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sick…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rangiku! Not now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll rush you back to\Nthe barracks, so hold it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.53,0:10:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…give me a break…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more.\NWe're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.49,0:10:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I warned you this would happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you, Rangiku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.49,0:10:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was fun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's got you so sentimental?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh boy…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never figured\Nyou'd get this big…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.43,0:12:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was you, after all, Kirikaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who was most\Ndissatisfied with your master!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have the ability to\Ntransform into mist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You used that power to\Nenter the bodies of others
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and suck away their\NSpiritual Pressure…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to grow this massive from\Nstealing the power
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.23,0:12:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of other Sword Beasts…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.95,0:12:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, c'mon, c'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.23,0:12:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He turned himself into mist!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.51,0:12:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was uncalled for!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is not the time.\NSo quit complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.95,0:13:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.15,0:13:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your backside is wide open.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.35,0:13:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that's as far you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.15,0:13:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you that you\Ndon't have a monopoly
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.68,0:13:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on sucking away\NSpiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.83,0:13:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.39,0:13:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't all have to come…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.11,0:13:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Undo your technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.23,0:14:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess this is as far as I can go…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.24,0:14:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Gonryomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Above you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.71,0:15:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Renji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.67,0:15:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakudo Number 63! Sajosabaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to transform into mist!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've put a stop to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the middle of a battle—\Ndon't let down your guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, pull yourself together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:15:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're ruining a pretty face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rangiku…why are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.43,0:16:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think we didn't realize\Nsomething was going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momo…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.66,0:16:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you come here for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the fool here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do\Nin your condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.57,0:16:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you are also reaching\Nyour limits, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.74,0:16:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.95,0:16:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, just concentrate\Non the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this Sword Beast's ability is\Ntoo dangerous for Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we came\Nwithout telling you…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swords alone… Soul Reapers alone…\Nare not enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only when we're paired together
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can we show our true power\Nfor the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you learn that lesson from\Nwhat happened to Muramasa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go doing things\Nby yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.51,0:17:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Renji…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right…we were wrong…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazeshini…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.45,0:17:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to take care\Nof this quickly, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So give me a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.59,0:17:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going after\Nthe Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sodenoshirayuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.43,0:17:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pierce!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:18:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reign over the Frosted Heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.43,0:18:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.55,0:18:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Hyorinmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do any more with\Nthe Spiritual Pressure I have left…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We told you—you're not alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Rukia…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be all right
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I are always together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.95,0:18:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Sodenoshirayuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.19,0:18:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dance, Sodenoshirayuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Tsuginomai Hakuren!\N– Tsuginomai Hakuren!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.51,0:18:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wabisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.87,0:18:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tobiume!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.39,0:18:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazeshini!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haineko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:18:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Raise your head!\N– Raise your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wabisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.19,0:19:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Snap!\N– Snap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.75,0:19:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tobiume!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Reap!\N– Reap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazeshini!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.47,0:19:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Growl!\N– Growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haineko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.99,0:19:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't transform into mist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's weakened considerably.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.36,0:19:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Renji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.93,0:19:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll give you our remaining\NSpiritual Pressure as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Renji… We threw all the feelings\Nwe had towards you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you've always answered\Nto those feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.43,0:19:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zabimaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.11,0:19:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Renji, it's been fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:19:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.31,0:20:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bankai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hihio Zabimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.31,0:20:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikotsu…taiho!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.27,0:20:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've all disappeared,\Nas we expected…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.83,0:20:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as the Sword Beast reached
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.43,0:20:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the limits of\Nits Spiritual Pressure,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Zanpakuto became\Ndepleted to the point
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.79,0:20:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where they could not maintain\Ntheir manifest forms…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their appearance was\Na temporary form
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,manifested through the medium\Nof Muramasa's powers…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.67,0:20:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They knew this would\Neventually happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:20:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.87,0:21:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to feel lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've simply returned to where\Nthey originally came from…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.84,0:21:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can always see them…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel their presence?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.63,0:21:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a very nostalgic feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.03,0:21:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though they're no longer\Nin those forms…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.27,0:21:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will always be\Ntogether with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Renji…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.15,0:21:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.11,0:21:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.99,0:21:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally over now…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.83,0:21:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.43,0:21:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back to the Seireitei.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.36,0:23:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The producers are finally done\Nwith shifting the story around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.16,0:23:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting,\NMaster Ulquiorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.33,0:23:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind if I have a cup of tea\Nbefore we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.35,0:23:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.59,0:23:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo's not here yet,\Nso take your time and enjoy…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.31,0:23:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.26,0:23:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.43,0:23:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you here, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awfully early!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.78,0:23:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have any scenes\Nand got bored!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.31,0:23:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point,\Nyou're the main star in name only.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.98,0:23:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so blunt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.22,0:23:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's get started\Nwith the next arc!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.67,0:23:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Ulquiorra's\Nstill having his tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.71,0:23:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when did you\Nbecome so selfish, Ichigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.87,0:24:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the reason why\Nno one treats you like a star!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.08,0:24:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's going too far…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.36,0:24:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.05,0:24:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– You're too slow.\N– Kurosaki! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.09,0:24:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,